### Do not push

- There is a reference project at root/near-jsonrpc-client-ts-reference/
- It is an example for cursor to use. This project is built from near-jsonrpc-client-ts-reference/ as an example.
- Cursor is not suppose to push near-jsonrpc-client-ts-reference/ to github repo.
- Should not be added to .gitignore either.
- Use it only locally as a reference. Should be ignored from git add when commiting other changes.
